title: 200: College Football Preview
itunes:title: 200: College Football Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks review a few NFL news notes from the past week before diving into the college football season with FOX analyst Joel Klatt. The guys wrap the show by picking the big matchups from the loaded opening weekend of college football.
